sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant OverviewUI as Dashboard Overview Page
    participant OverviewAPI as GET /api/overview
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Admin->>OverviewUI: Open /dashboard
    OverviewUI->>OverviewAPI: Request aggregate metrics
    OverviewAPI->>DB: Count blogs, projects, messages, subscribers
    OverviewAPI->>DB: Read top viewed entries and recent inbox items
    DB-->>OverviewAPI: Aggregate datasets
    OverviewAPI-->>OverviewUI: KPI payload and widgets data
    OverviewUI-->>Admin: Render cards, top content, inbox snapshot
